divs: Sighting DetailsI took this photo because I truly thought at first, that is was a UFO. After seeing several cigar shaped UFOs reported with a black black dot on the middle, I think they are talking about this kind of airplane, which someone told me was a DC9. I was on the freeway when this one passed across and above,. I did not hear a sound but I could see that the wings were very short and at first site it seemed like i did not have them. This does not mean that there may be real UFOs with this shape, but really, I doubt that they could be exacty like this airplane, as described several times in the last few months.
Summary: It's what coudl e construed as a cigar shaped UFO
